gomodel:SYNGO_5395  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1: S1PR5 was detected in synaptosomal biochemical fractions prepared from mouse cortex, with enrichment in the synaptosome-subfraction that excludes the active zone (membrane) and minor detection in the active zone fraction (similar to synaptosome).. Experimental description: M&M: \"Synaptosomal fractionation was modified from Morato et al. [37]. Briefly, the mouse cortex was homogenized in 1 mL of isolation buffer ...\"\n\nantibody:\nRabbit anti-S1PR5, 1:500 (WB)/1:250 (IFn)/1:100 (IFs), Novus (NBP2-24,712)" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
